original_title: 不良番長 猪の鹿お蝶
overview: Kosaka Hiroshi is a small time swindler and the boss of a motorcycle gang in  Shinjuku. Living only to make money, he never made the big time until he gets  involved with a Yakuza's daughter. But when he gets involved in a scheme to  blackmail a Yakuza gang and a land developer, he realizes he's gone way over his  head…
title: Delinquent Boss: Wolves of the City
